==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Inapplicable
<hw>In*ap"pli*ca*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>in-</ets> not + <ets>applicable</ets>.]</ety> <def>Not applicable;
incapable of being applied; not adapted; not suitable; <as>as, the
argument is <ex>inapplicable</ex> to the case</as>.</def> <rj><au>J. S.
Mill.</au></rj></p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- Unsuitable; unsuited; unadapted; inappropriate;
inapposite; irrelevant.</syn></p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>In*ap"pli*ca*ble*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos> --
<wf>In*ap"pli*ca*bly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Inapplication</ent>⟦br⟧
